# ☁️ Cloud Task Manager API

A simple REST API built with Node.js and hosted on Microsoft Azure. Users can register, log in, and manage personal task lists with optional file uploads stored in Azure Blob Storage.

### 🔧 Tech Stack
- Node.js + Express
- Azure SQL Database
- Azure Blob Storage
- JWT Authentication
- Azure App Service (Deployment)

### 🌐 Live Demo
🚀 [Live API Endpoint](https://your-api.azurewebsites.net)  
📄 [Swagger Docs](https://your-api.azurewebsites.net/docs)

### 📁 Sample Request
```bash
POST /tasks
Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
Body: {
  "title": "Finish Azure Project",
  "description": "Push to GitHub"
}
